- link \"Ben Steed\" [ref=e59]:\n      - /url: http://bensteed.com\n    - text: and became part of the\n    - link \"Heartlight\" [ref=e60]:\n      - /url: https://www.heartlight.org\n    - text: Network in 2000.\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"Heartlight Logo\" [ref=e61]:\n      - /url: https://www.heartlight.org\n      - img \"Heartlight Logo\"\n  - heading \"More Daily Devos:\" [ref=e62] [level=3]\n  - heading \"Quotemeal\" [ref=e63] [level=4]:\n    - link \"Quotemeal\" [ref=e64]:\n      - /url: http://www.heartlight.org/cgi-shl/quotemeal.cgi\n  - text: A daily dose of Christian quotes to inspire and encourage.\n  - link \"Read Today's 'Quotemeal' Devotional\" [ref=e65]:\n    - /url: https://www.heartlight.org/cgi-shl/quotemeal.cgi?day=20260428\n    - img \"Read Today's 'Quotemeal' Devotional\"\n  - text: \"Quote by Miguel de Unamuno:\"\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"\\\" [ref=e66]Cure yourself of the condition of bothering about how you look to other people. Be concerned only . . . with the idea God has of you.\\\"\":\n      - /url: https://www.heartlight.org/cgi-shl/quotemeal.cgi?day=20260428\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"Subscribe to Quotemeal\" [ref=e67]:\n      - /url: https://www.verseoftheday.com/subscribe.php?lang=qm&KeepThis=true&TB_iframe=true&height=300&width=445\n      - img\n      - text: Subscribe to Quotemeal\n  - heading \"Passion for Praise\" [ref=e68] [level=4]:\n    - link \"Passion for Praise\" [ref=e69]:\n      - /url: http://www.heartlight.org/cgi-shl/passionforpraise.cgi\n  - text: A daily passage of Scripture emphasizing praise to our God.\n  - link \"Read Today's 'Passion for Praise' Devotional\" [ref=e70]:\n    - /url: https://www.heartlight.org/cgi-shl/passionforpraise.cgi?day=20260428\n    - img \"Read Today's 'Passion for Praise' Devotional\"\n  - text: \"'He Does Not Ignore Their Cries' (Ps. 9:11-12)\"\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"\\\" [ref=e71] [nth=1]Sing praises to the Lord who reigns ... Tell the world about his unforgettable deeds. For he who avenges murder cares for the helpless. He does not...\\\"\":\n      - /url: https://www.heartlight.org/cgi-shl/passionforpraise.cgi?day=20260428\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"Subscribe to Passion for Praise\" [ref=e72]:\n      - /url: https://www.verseoftheday.com/subscribe.php?lang=pfp&KeepThis=true&TB_iframe=true&height=300&width=445\n      - img\n      - text: Subscribe to Passion for Praise\n  - heading \"Morning & Evening\" [ref=e73] [level=4]:\n    - link \"Morning & Evening\" [ref=e74]:\n      - /url: http://www.heartlight.org/spurgeon/\n  - text: The classic twice-daily devotional from Charles H. Spurgeon.\n  - link \"Read Today's 'Morning & Evening' Devotional\" [ref=e75]:\n    - /url: https://www.heartlight.org/spurgeon/0428-am.html\n    - img \"Read Today's 'Morning & Evening' Devotional\"\n  - text: \"Morning Thought: Psalms 119:49\"\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"\\\" [ref=e76] [nth=2]Whatever your especial need may be, you may readily find some promise in the Bible suited to it. Are you faint and feeble because your way is rough...\\\"\":\n      - /url: https://www.heartlight.org/spurgeon/0428-am.html\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"Subscribe to Morning & Evening\" [ref=e77]:\n      - /url: https://www.verseoftheday.com/subscribe.php?lang=me&KeepThis=true&TB_iframe=true&height=300&width=445\n      - img\n      - text: Subscribe to Morning & Evening\n  - heading \"Translations\" [ref=e78] [level=3]\n  - list:\n    - listitem:\n      - link \"English\" [ref=e79]:\n        - /url: /en/\n    - listitem:\n      - link \"中文\" [ref=e80]:\n        - /url: /cn/\n    - listitem:\n      - link \"Deutsch\" [ref=e81]:\n        - /url: /de/\n    - listitem:\n      - link \"Español\" [ref=e82]:\n        - /url: /es/\n    - listitem:\n      - link \"Français\" [ref=e83]:\n        - /url: /fr/\n    - listitem:\n      - link \"한국어\" [ref=e84]:\n        - /url: /ko/\n    - listitem:\n      - link \"Русский\" [ref=e85]:\n        - /url: /ru/\n    - listitem:\n  