{"type":"message","id":"9f69056d","parentId":"13fe8f0e","timestamp":"2026-04-28T09:33:24.461Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The bills file is `bills.json`, not `bills_april_2026.json`. Let me run the correct command to get bills. Also I need to get emails. Let me check the gog skill for emails.","thinkingSignature":"09b3d0f6cab025237a76476df8259872a4fc5a81d3cbda6c62e0f20ee1afce61"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7hiezm7hnzr8_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"import json; bills=json.load(open('/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/data/bills.json')); from datetime import datetime; today=datetime.now(); [print(f'• {b[\\\"name\\\"]} — {b[\\\"dueDate\\\"][5:]} — \\${b[\\\"amount\\\"]:.2f} [{\\\"✅ PAID\\\" if b.get(\\\"paid\\\") else \\\"⚠️ DUE\\\"}]') for b in bills if datetime.strptime(b['dueDate'],'%Y-%m-%d')<=today+__import__('datetime').timedelta(days=7)]\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7hiezm7hnzr8_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/gog/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":8085,"output":243,"cacheRead":20865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29193,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777368799409,"responseId":"063fb1df15e923fb9a310bccdad40103"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0936cf05","parentId":"9f69056d","timestamp":"2026-04-28T09:33:24.547Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_7hiezm7hnzr8_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"• Capitol One Quicksilver — 03-27 — $411.00 [✅ PAID]\n• Chase — 03-28 — $74.00 [✅ PAID]\n• Flex — 03-31 — $355.14 [✅ PAID]\n• Apple Card — 03-31 — $60.00 [✅ PAID]\n• T-Mobile — 03-25 — $98.29 [✅ PAID]\n• Capitol One Quicksilver — 04-15 — $25.00 [✅ PAID]\n• Discover — 04-15 — $25.00 [✅ PAID]\n• GEICO — 04-15 — $187.25 [✅ PAID]\n• Capital One Quicksilver — 04-27 — $96.00 [⚠️ DUE]"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":72,"aggregated":"• Capitol One Quicksilver — 03-27 — $411.00 [✅ PAID]\n• Chase — 03-28 — $74.00 [✅ PAID]\n• Flex — 03-31 — $355.14 [✅ PAID]\n• Apple Card — 03-31 — $60.00 [✅ PAID]\n• T-Mobile — 03-25 — $98.29 [✅ PAID]\n• Capitol One Quicksilver — 04-15 — $25.00 [✅ PAID]\n• Discover — 04-15 — $25.00 [✅ PAID]\n• GEICO — 04-15 — $187.25 [✅ PAID]\n• Capital One Quicksilver — 04-27 — $96.00 [⚠️ DUE]","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777368804547}}
{"type":"message","id":"7f3c5843","parentId":"0936cf05","timestamp":"2026-04-28T09:33:24.548Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_7hiezm7hnzr8_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: gog\ndescription: Google Workspace CLI for Gmail, Calendar, Drive, Contacts, Sheets, and Docs.\nhomepage: https://gogcli.sh\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"emoji\": \"🎮\",\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"gog\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"brew\",\n              \"kind\": \"brew\",\n              \"formula\": \"steipete/tap/gogcli\",\n              \"bins\": [\"gog\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install gog (brew)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# gog\n\nUse `gog` for Gmail/Calendar/Drive/Contacts/Sheets/Docs. Requires OAuth setup.\n\nSetup (once)\n\n- `gog auth credentials /path/to/client_secret.json`\n- `gog auth add you@gmail.com --services gmail,calendar,drive,contacts,docs,sheets`\n- `gog auth list`\n\nCommon commands\n\n- Gmail search: `gog gmail search 'newer_than:7d' --max 10`\n- Gmail messages search (per email, ignores threading): `gog gmail messages search \"in:inbox from:ryanair.com\" --max 20 --account you@example.com`\n- Gmail send (plain): `gog gmail send --to a@b.com --subject \"Hi\" --body \"Hello\"`\n- Gmail send (multi-line): `gog gmail send --to a@b.com --subject \"Hi\" --body-file ./message.txt`\n- Gmail send (stdin): `gog gmail send --to a@b.com --subject \"Hi\" --body-file -`\n- Gmail send (HTML): `gog gmail send --to a@b.com --subject \"Hi\" --body-html \"<p>Hello</p>\"`\n- Gmail draft: `gog gmail drafts create --to a@b.com --subject \"Hi\" --body-file ./message.txt`\n- Gmail send draft: `gog gmail drafts send <draftId>`\n- Gmail reply: `gog gmail send --to a@b.com --subject \"Re: Hi\" --body \"Reply\" --reply-to-message-id <msgId>`\n- Calendar list events: `gog calendar events <calendarId> --from <iso> --to <iso>`\n- Calendar create event: `gog calendar create <calendarId> --summary \"Title\" --from <iso> --to <iso>`\n- Calendar create with color: `gog calendar create <calendarId> --summary \"Title\" --from <iso> --to <iso> --event-color 7`\n- Calendar update event: `gog calendar update <calendarId> <eventId> --summary \"New Title\" --event-color 4`\n- Calendar show colors: `gog calendar colors`\n- Drive search: `gog drive search \"query\" --max 10`\n- Contacts: `gog contacts list --max 20`\n- Sheets get: `gog sheets get <sheetId> \"Tab!A1:D10\" --json`\n- Sheets update: `gog sheets update <sheetId> \"Tab!A1:B2\" --values-json '[[\"A\",\"B\"],[\"1\",\"2\"]]' --input USER_ENTERED`\n- Sheets append: `gog sheets append <sheetId> \"Tab!A:C\" --values-json '[[\"x\",\"y\",\"z\"]]' --insert INSERT_ROWS`\n- Sheets clear: `gog sheets clear <sheetId> \"Tab!A2:Z\"`\n- Sheets metadata: `gog sheets metadata <sheetId> --json`\n- Docs export: `gog docs export <docId> --format txt --out /tmp/doc.txt`\n- Docs cat: `gog docs cat <docId>`\n\nCalendar Colors\n\n- Use `gog calendar colors` to see all available event colors (IDs 1-11)\n- Add colors to events with `--event-color <id>` flag\n- Event color IDs (from `gog calendar colors` output):\n  - 1: #a4bdfc\n  - 2: #7ae7bf\n  - 3: #dbadff\n  - 4: #ff887c\n  - 5: #fbd75b\n  - 6: #ffb878\n  - 7: #46d6db\n  - 8: #e1e1e1\n  - 9: #5484ed\n  - 10: #51b749\n  - 11: #dc2127\n\nEmail Formatting\n\n- Prefer plain text. Use `--body-file` for multi-paragraph messages (or `--body-file -` for stdin).\n- Same `--body-file` pattern works for drafts and replies.\n- `--body` does not unescape `\\n`. If you need inline newlines, use a heredoc or `$'Line 1\\n\\nLine 2'`.\n- Use `--body-html` only when you need rich formatting.\n- HTML tags: `<p>` for paragraphs, `<br>` for line breaks, `<strong>` for bold, `<em>` for italic, `<a href=\"url\">` for links, `<ul>`/`<li>` for lists.\n- Example (plain text via stdin):\n\n  ```bash\n  gog gmail send --to recipient@example.com \\\n    --subject \"Meeting Follow-up\" \\\n    --body-file - <<'EOF'\n  Hi Name,\n\n  Thanks for meeting today. Next steps:\n  - Item one\n  - Item two\n\n  Best regards,\n  Your Name\n  EOF\n  ```\n\n- Example (HTML list):\n  ```bash\n  gog gmail send --to recipient@example.com \\\n    --subject \"Meeting Follow-up\" \\\n    --body-html \"<p>Hi Name,</p><p>Thanks for meeting today. Here are the next steps:</p><ul><li>Item one</li><li>Item two</li></ul><p>Best regards,<br>Your Name</p>\"\n  ```\n\nNotes\n\n- Set `GOG_ACCOUNT=you@gmail.com` to avoid repeating `--account`.\n- For scripting, prefer `--json` plus `--no-input`.\n- Sheets values can be passed via `--values-json` (recommended) or as inline rows.\n- Docs supports export/cat/copy. In-place edits require a Docs API client (not in gog).\n- Confirm before sending mail or creating events.\n- `gog gmail search` returns one row per thread; use `gog gmail messages search` when you need every individual email returned separately.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777368804547}}
{"type":"message","id":"04856043","parentId":"7f3c5843","timestamp":"2026-04-28T09:33:29.186Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me get emails from yesterday and today via gog. The date is April 28, 2026, so I need emails from April 27 and April 28.","thinkingSignature":"799e11088f2eee9c06fcd7172c962acf7a2b7fcef154f47b5906449efcd26acb"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0le0226thwpt_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"gog gmail search 'after:2026/04/27' --max 20 2>/dev/null || echo \"GOG_FAILED\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":9897,"output":91,"cacheRead":20865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30853,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777368804548,"responseId":"063fb1e45e7bfdaa4cd143569024964a"}}
