{"type":"message","id":"e27efb54","parentId":"e44d3350","timestamp":"2026-04-28T09:33:46.595Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have all the data I need. Let me compile the morning brief and send it section by section.\n\n**Section 1 - Header:**\n```\nGood morning, Bobby! ☀️\n\nTuesday, April 28, 2026\n\nHere's what we've got going on for today…\n```\n\n**Section 2 - Weather:**\n```\n🌤️ Knoxville Weather — April 28\n\nNOW: 65° (feels like 65°)\nHIGH: 77° | LOW: 59°\nWIND: 4mph | HUMIDITY: 73% | UV: 0 (Low) | RAIN: 0%\n\n⏰ HOUR BY HOUR:\n\n\n```\n\nNow I'm looking at the hourly breakdown from 9AM through 9PM with temperatures ranging from 65° up to 76°, then cooling back down. The day looks clear with mostly sunny to partly cloudy conditions, so short sleeves will be fine.\n\nMoving into calendar events and reminders for the week, I see Chase due today at 9:00 AM for $74, Apple Card coming up on 4/30 for $64, and Affirm Marriott on 5/2 for $129.59. There's also an incomplete bill for Capital One Quicksilver due on 4/27 for $96 that still needs attention.\n\n```\n📅 YOUR WEEK (April 28 — May 4)\n\nTUESDAY April 28:\n• Chase — $74.00 (Family Calendar) — 9:00 AM\n• ⚠️ Capital One Quicksilver — $96.00 — DUE TODAY\n\nWEDNESDAY April 29:\n• Apple Card — $64.00 (Family Calendar) — 9:00 AM\n\nTHURSDAY April 30:\n• Free day!\n\nFRIDAY May 1:\n• Free day!\n\nSATURDAY May 2:\n• Affirm Marriott — $129.59 (Family Calendar) — 9:00 AM\n\nSUNDAY May 3:\n• Free day!\n\nMONDAY May 4:\n• Free day!\n\nTUESDAY May 5:\n• Cinco de Mayo (US Holidays)\n\n---\n\n💡 BASED ON YOUR SCHEDULE: The Capital One Quicksilver bill for $96 is marked as due today and needs payment. Also, there's an apartment email from Angelina at Walkway Realty that appears to be important and flagged for follow-up. For today, I should focus on sending that apartment inquiry response to Angelina and handling the payment.","thinkingSignature":"16423fac2a88febf7069cdad03402143bc8bdd20463626eeb06bbee590640459"},{"type":"text","text":"Now I have all the data. Let me send the 7 sections one at a time to Telegram.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_u2xt7psyab4x_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"telegram","target":"8212808444","message":"Good morning, Bobby! ☀️\n\nTuesday, April 28, 2026\n\nHere's what we've got going on for today…"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":11266,"output":613,"cacheRead":20865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32744,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777368810722,"responseId":"063fb1eaca042a177e5937b0984d6512"}}
